	  - re-indent
	  - use begins_with()
	more cleanup
	cleanup
	isRemovableDrive() doesn't check isRemovableUsb() anymore allowing more
	usb
	removable drives (esp. some usb keys declared as memory cards (0x0c76
	0x0005))

