	* Makefile: Use bash in stage2 on IA-64

	* mdk-stage1/Makefile: Fix merge from amd64-branch

	* rescue/list.x86_64, rescue/list: Merge with amd64-branch (rpm libdir is
	always /usr/lib/rpm, update lists)

