2003/01/30  Pixel  <pixel@mandrakesoft.com>

	* install_interactive.pm: drop $o->{lnx4win} handling
	add isFat_or_NTFS() and use it where possible instead of isFat() since
	Windows
	is now using ntfs, not only Windows NT

