	* mouse.pm: 
	  - don't display "To activate the mouse, MOVE YOUR WHEEL!" when not
	install
	  - don't display "Please test the mouse" either
	allow to not mess with X config auxmouse
	(that way mousedrake doesn't need to care about it)
