	* Xconfigurator_consts.pm: removed ugly Modeline 1024x768 which causes
	trouble to XFree86 4.1.0.

	* Xconfigurator.pm: fix for missing Xinerama for Matrox cards.
	fix for Matrox G550 support, now add DRI support.
